Rapper Cardi B set to release brand new single ’Up’. On Sunday,January 31 2021, Cardi tweeted a video with the caption “I got an announcement to make tomorrow” and a loud-speaker emoji, so it’s safe to say this was her big news. After teasing the big announcement, Cardi B has revealed that her new single “Up” will drop Friday, February 5, 2021. She shared the artwork, which features her swinging in a bubble chair while suspended over a pool. “My new single ‘UP’ drops this Friday! LETS GOOOOOO! #Up,” she captioned. “Up” marks the follow-up to Cardi’s hit single “WAP” with Megan Thee Stallion, which topped the Billboard Hot 100 and was certified triple platinum.